longBusinessSummary: Shriram Properties Limited operates as a real estate development company in India. The company engages in the business of construction, development, and sale of housing projects. It also develops residential projects, including mid-market and affordable, mid-market premium, and luxury housing projects, as well as commercial and plotted development projects. The company was founded in 1995 and is based in Bengaluru, India.
